<p>The <code>@remaining</code> property returns the number of iterations remaining after the current one.</p>

<h2>Remaining Count</h2>
<pre>{open}users{close}
  {open}$name{close} ({open}@remaining{close} more to go)
{open}/users{close}</pre>

<p>Result:</p>
<div>
{users}
  {$name} ({@remaining} more to go)<br>
{/users}
</div>

<h2>Conditional on Remaining</h2>
<pre>{open}colors{close}
  {open}$colors{close}
  {open}if @remaining gt 0{close}
    - {open}@remaining{close} remaining
  {open}else{close}
    - Done!
  {open}/if{close}
{open}/colors{close}</pre>

<p>Result:</p>
<div>
{colors}
  {$colors}
  {if @remaining gt 0}
    - {@remaining} remaining
  {else}
    - Done!
  {/if}
  <br>
{/colors}
</div>
